column4: what do you want to know?
i cannot preview and natilius does not recognize .png files
i have to open it with image viewer or gthumb
have you checked nautilus settings? Edit-Preferences-Preview
yea and i have deleted .nautilus and .thumbnails
does it log any error messages in ~/.xsession-errors?
when you deleted ~/.nautilus, was it running at the time?
yeah but i have since restarted
log out, start a failsafe session and delete .nautilus from there. Otherwise nautilus recreates the original when it exits (I believe)
